item.description: IV. Conclusion This Commonly Mispelled Name Has Stumped Even the Smartest Spellers - Find Out How to Spell ‘Eloise’ Here! The name Eloise is a beautiful, unique name, but it can be difficult to spell. Even the smartest spellers have been stumped by this commonly mispelled name. This article will look at the reasons why Eloise is so difficult to spell, and provide tips for spelling it correctly. Definition of Eloise Eloise is a French name derived from the German name “Helewidis”, which means “widely known”.
